            Explore UIC Business
          Heading link



 
Copy link









            Undergraduate Programs
          
Explore core competencies of business fundamentals with real-world experience through valuable Chicago businesses connections.






            Graduate Programs
          
MBA and six specialized master’s degrees combine world-class academic and research credentials with outstanding business leadership experience to yield a high ROI.






            Doctoral Programs
          
Study with renowned experts at a Research 1 institution.






            Alumni
          
Volunteer with students, connect with fellow alumni, support your alma mater.










